<bibRefCitation id="EFAA1CF9FFB4F930FB01FD23FF4DFC87" author="Lackner, T. &amp; Pavicevic, D." pageId="38" pageNumber="235" pagination="423 - 426" refId="ref74144" refString="Lackner, T. &amp; Pavicevic, D. (2008) Faunistic note on newly recorded and rare species of Histeridae from Serbia (Coleoptera). In: Pavicevic, D. &amp; Perreau, M. (Eds), Advances in the studies of the fauna of the Balkan Peninsula. Papers dedicated to the memory of Guido Nonveiller. Institute for Nature Conservation of Serbia, Belgrade, Monograph 22, pp. 423 - 426." type="journal article" year="2008">Lackner &amp; Pavićević 2008</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B846108FFB4F930FF5BFCFEFD4DFC48" blockId="38.[151,1436,294,2017]" pageId="38" pageNumber="235">
<emphasis id="B94FBD1AFFB4F930FF5BFCFEFE8BFCE0" bold="true" box="[196,273,820,846]" pageId="38" pageNumber="235">Notes.</emphasis>
